title: American Car - March 2014  UK
description:
American Car - March 2014  UK

116 Pages | True PDF | English | 41 MB 


Inside American Car Magazine you'll find what our reader feedback has told us readers want to see - UK-based, street-legal American cars and trucks, reportage from shows large and small across the country, race reports from events and series at all the UK's drag strips, and technical articles from the most basic to the most complex. New or old, stock or modified, from the simplest to the most radical, and from the tightest budget to the six-figure dream car, if it's an American car (or truck), you'll find it in American Car Magazine.
